<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:28
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='137000' id='t-137000'>So I'm very excited to be able
to show you those images</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='140000' id='t-140000'>and a cross-section of my work
that I've done on the polar regions.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='142000' id='t-142000'>Please enjoy.</span>
</span>
</p>
