<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:29
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='738000' id='t-738000'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:31
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='740000' id='t-740000'>So after five days of crossing
the Drake Passage --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='743000' id='t-743000'>isn't that beautiful --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='746000' id='t-746000'>after five days of crossing
the Drake Passage,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='749000' id='t-749000'>we have finally arrived at Antarctica.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='751000' id='t-751000'>I'm with my Swedish assistant and guide.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='753000' id='t-753000'>His name is Goran Ehlme
from Sweden -- Goran.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='757000' id='t-757000'>And he has a lot of experience
with leopard seals. I have never seen one.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='760000' id='t-760000'>So we come around the cove
