<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='763000' id='t-763000'>and there's this monstrous leopard seal.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='765000' id='t-765000'>And even in his voice, he goes,
&quot;That's a bloody big seal, ya.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='767000' id='t-767000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='769000' id='t-769000'>And this seal is taking
