<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='776000' id='t-776000'>so it can eat the meat off the bones,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='779000' id='t-779000'>and then it goes off and gets another one.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:12
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='781000' id='t-781000'>And so this leopard seal
grabbed another penguin,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='783000' id='t-783000'>came under the boat, the Zodiac,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='785000' id='t-785000'>starting hitting the hull of the boat.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='787000' id='t-787000'>And we're trying to not fall in the water.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='789000' id='t-789000'>And we sit down,
