<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='792000' id='t-792000'>&quot;This is a good seal, ya.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='794000' id='t-794000'>It's time for you to get in the water.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='796000' id='t-796000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='799000' id='t-799000'>And I looked at Goran,
