<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='810000' id='t-810000'>And you purposed this stupid story
to National Geographic.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='812000' id='t-812000'>And now you've got to deliver.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='814000' id='t-814000'>And you can't publish excuses.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
