13:47
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='816000' id='t-816000'>So I had such dry mouth --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='818000' id='t-818000'>probably not as bad as now --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='820000' id='t-820000'>but I had such, such dry mouth.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='824000' id='t-824000'>And my legs were just trembling.
