<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='827000' id='t-827000'>I put my flippers on.
I could barely part my lips.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='829000' id='t-829000'>I put my snorkel in my mouth,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='831000' id='t-831000'>and I rolled over the side
