<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='834000' id='t-834000'>And this was the first thing she did.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='836000' id='t-836000'>She came racing up to me,
engulfed my whole camera --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='839000' id='t-839000'>and her teeth are up here
