<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='924000' id='t-924000'>so she brought me dead penguins.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='926000' id='t-926000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='929000' id='t-929000'>Now I've got four or five penguins
